# Create a filter returning those issues;
# Add the *Filter Results* gadget to the dashboard;
# Pass between the results (from 1-10 to 11-20 to 21-30 and so on).

h3. Expected Results:
The gadget's window would resize automatically to adjust to the size of the summaries returned.

h3. Actual Results:
The gadget does not correctly adjust the size automatically, which causes a blank space in the bottom of the gadget:
